line_2: From bursting streams, and burning rocks,

line_1: " I hate thee, beast; thy look my spirit shocks;
line_2: "Oh! that I saw thee starving in the stocks!"

line_1: Ye Cupids, Cloes, Phillis's, or Shocks,
line_2: Ye who defend the houshold, or the flocks:

line_1: This view my forward zeal so shocks,
line_2: In vain they hold the money-box.
